author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile floor tip…I use Schluter metal profiles for tile floors. They protect the tile from chipping. I slide Barwalt wedges underneath the tiles. This compresses the profile tight against the tile. Once the mortar cures, I remove the wedges 👍🏽🔥#tile #tilefloor #homerenovation #homerenovationideas
